Description: MX Tools Launcher for MX Linux
 MX Tools is a graphical utility that provides a centralized launcher for
 accessing various MX Linux configuration and system management tools.
 It offers a user-friendly interface for:
  * System maintenance and repair
  * Software installation and management
  * Hardware configuration
  * System customization
